description: Stata teffects psmatch 验证数据 (Story 4.1)

commands.44: teffects psmatch (y_44) (g4 x1 x2) if f04, atet
commands.45: teffects psmatch (y_45) (g4 x1 x2) if f05 & ~g5, atet
commands.46: teffects psmatch (y_46) (g4 x1 x2) if f06 & (g5 + g6 != 1), atet
commands.55: teffects psmatch (y_55) (g5 x1 x2) if f05 & ~g4, atet
commands.56: teffects psmatch (y_56) (g5 x1 x2) if f06 & (g4 + g6 != 1), atet
commands.66: teffects psmatch (y_66) (g6 x1 x2) if f06 & (g4 + g5 != 1), atet

notes: 所有估计使用1个最近邻匹配 (nn=1)
teffects psmatch 默认使用有放回匹配
